ghost-role-information-centurion-asakim-name = Asakim Centurion
ghost-role-information-centurion-asakim-description = An elite pre-fracture genetically enhanced warrior awakened with an Asakim detachment.
ghost-role-information-centurion-asakim-rules =
    You are an [color=#ff3db1][bold]Asakim Centurion[/bold][/color], a senior warrior among pre-fracture genetically engineered super soldiers. Your allies are other Asakim warriors and the [color=#ff3db1]ADS fleet[/color].
    Your objectives are to [color=red]capture and hold points of interest[/color], protect pre-fracture technology, and direct other Asakim operating in the sector.
    Reading the guidebook is [color=red][bold]mandatory for this role[/bold][/color].
    You do not remember your previous life or anything learned while you were a ghost.

ghost-role-information-prefect-asakim-name = Asakim Prefect
ghost-role-information-prefect-asakim-description = A senior pre-fracture command officer awakened alongside an Asakim detachment.
ghost-role-information-prefect-asakim-rules =
    You are an [color=#ff3db1][bold]Asakim Prefect[/bold][/color], a senior field officer among pre-fracture genetically engineered super soldiers. Your allies are other Asakim warriors and the [color=#ff3db1]ADS fleet[/color].
    Your objectives are to [color=red]set the detachment's strategy, coordinate centurions, and secure key points across the sector[/color] without wasting the expedition in reckless attacks.
    You outrank centurions in the field chain of command and act as the senior available infantry officer unless a higher imperial rank is present.
    Reading the guidebook is [color=red][bold]mandatory for this role[/bold][/color].
    You do not remember your previous life or anything learned while you were a ghost.

ghost-role-information-asakim-redacted-borg = Personal Protection Operator
ghost-role-information-asakim-redacted-borg-description = A synthetic bodyguard assigned to protect the officer corps of the Khs'i-Ra Empire.

ghost-role-information-asakim-fighter-borg = Assault System Operator
ghost-role-information-asakim-fighter-borg-description =  A synthetic stormtrooper of the Khs'i-Ra Empire.
